\
Since the scandal came to light it could be said people are more aware of how their personal info and data may be used\
\
Facebook who have tried to reassure their users that this will never happen again, with Mark Zuckerberg welcoming regulation from the EU. The EU has introduced GDPR AND In the US some states have drafted new laws that requires data brokers which buy and sell data from third parties to register with the state.\cf0 \
\
 \
