\cf7 Informed Consent\
\
The basis of any regulation has to involve the idea of informed consent, it could be said it people loured into a false sense of privacy and gave away their data too easily.\
\
Social media companies must be more explicit in telling users how their data is stored and any third parties who may be using the data.\
